  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMETSTRIKER DX</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/cae070d64a2a58f887af11fc24e88c94.poster.avif?t=1773951304\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/cae070d64a2a58f887af11fc24e88c94.webm?t=1773951304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/cae070d64a2a58f887af11fc24e88c94.mp4?t=1773951304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Striker, come in!</h2>A world devouring space station has set its sights on your planet! Help Lt. Striker<strong> boost through danger</strong> and <strong>blast the bad guys</strong> on his journey to recover the Ancient Power Cores, the only hope against this cosmic menace! This arcade-style shooter delivers <strong>constant action, beautiful sights to see and a super crisp soundtrack!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/d7f0ff1e3bb4d48f0688b97520a36cfd.poster.avif?t=1773951304\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/d7f0ff1e3bb4d48f0688b97520a36cfd.webm?t=1773951304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/d7f0ff1e3bb4d48f0688b97520a36cfd.mp4?t=1773951304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/ae088cacf8c1cf63cc7ce121a8348682.webp?t=1773951304\" width=600 height=26 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/380cd908c21a5e7bfb0f70e01bb2686e.webp?t=1773951304\" width=600 height=43 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Easy to learn three button combat</strong> allows you to shoot left or right, and use your boosters to <strong>invincibly dodge in any direction!</strong><br></li><li><strong>5 levels with branching paths</strong> so you can choose your favorites on subsequent playthroughs!<br></li><li><strong>Every level is packed with a variety of new enemies</strong> and hazards to learn, as well as minibosses and bosses to fight!<br></li><li><strong>4 difficulties</strong> with unique stage layouts and enemy behaviors, so the game is fun for chill or hardcore players!<br></li><li><strong>5 unlockable characters</strong>, all with different equipment and playstyles!<br></li><li><strong>\"Labyrinth Mode\" </strong>: Play a procedurally created campaign assembled from TONS of handcrafted rooms in this unlockable mode!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/1316df87f97ca845aa2996c849be0f0b.webp?t=1773951304\" width=600 height=43 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/d7297ff212238e88dc06e68e1084871f.poster.avif?t=1773951304\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/d7297ff212238e88dc06e68e1084871f.webm?t=1773951304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/d7297ff212238e88dc06e68e1084871f.mp4?t=1773951304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Two player local co-op for ALL game modes!</strong><br></li><li><strong>\"Challenge Mode\"</strong> : Go for S-Ranks in <strong>over fifty unique bite-sized challenge levels</strong> in this unlockable mode!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/ae088cacf8c1cf63cc7ce121a8348682.webp?t=1773951304\" width=600 height=26 /></span><br><strong><i>Only you can help Lt. Striker on his mission! The world is counting on you! Good luck!</i></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/808e9c228c9f7aa82970715d07c02444.poster.avif?t=1773951304\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/808e9c228c9f7aa82970715d07c02444.webm?t=1773951304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/701040/extras/808e9c228c9f7aa82970715d07c02444.mp4?t=1773951304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
